{"tid":324210,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"又重溫左一拳超人","createTime":"2017-07-16T09:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T17:03:17.000Z","uid":25340,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"679c621267e33a3f0963fec2d85cc86ecd5fc062","tid":324210,"uid":25340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"其實波羅斯死前可以遇到琦玉真係一種福氣黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢等於宇宙中既琦玉又係搵唔到對手<br />\n死前可以同琦玉打一場真係死而無憾<br />\n見到佢可以解脫真係抵佢開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/170332_370daf018582fee07e2da1c8137fd05b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F170332_370daf018582fee07e2da1c8137fd05b.jpg&h=9e7e3f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相反留低嘅琦玉其實好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望琦玉都可以搵到一個贏到自己嘅人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw我諗本身波羅斯勢均力敵嘅對手應該係爆破<br />\n因為個預言係二十年前<br />\n而龍卷細個 姐係十八年前 爆破曾經救過龍卷<br />\n所以個時間都幾吻合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26e27ab35889798c213bb4913bd0cf02cd3da77","tid":324210,"uid":91196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"勢均力敵既對手唔係講緊餓狼咩"},{"pid":"270bb0d74a6a7c5356937c7cb85d31ac27a474c6","tid":324210,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"巴打用緊咩app"},{"pid":"205179fda784fc77eea1e73f304d935be92b634f","tid":324210,"uid":25340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勢均力敵既對手唔係講緊餓狼咩</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係<br />\n因為二十年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47213fb647663f6ea608264e445fb3f615d6cf94","tid":324210,"uid":25340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:31:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打用緊咩app</blockquote><br />\n漫畫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371e4e19bb3a197e7ac3eac607a85ae40978123b","tid":324210,"uid":106614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"預言又唔一定講個陣既"}]}